{"tid":1094657,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黑警馬振康 林偉榮非法殺死的士司機幾時審？","createTime":"2019-04-06T12:45:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-07T02:45:23.000Z","uid":9193,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"89fc72734ee8dc97987a7a66d0a500a2d280335c","tid":1094657,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T12:45:10.000Z","msg":"陪審團作出3比2大比數裁決，判定司機死於「不合法被殺」，並向警方作出4項建議，包括在衝鋒車內加裝具錄音功能的閉路電視；培訓警員搬抬被捕人士上警車的技巧；除非被捕者拒絕，否則警方應盡快通知其家屬；如警員意識到於拘捕過程中，可能傷到被捕者應盡快通知醫護人員，並詳述受傷情況。<br />\n<br />\n65歲的士司機陳輝旺，2012年11月因車資問題和乘客爭執，被警方拘捕。警員一度箍頸將他扯上車，事後頸椎受傷全身癱瘓，一個月後因併發症死亡。死因庭陪審團裁定，司機死於不合法被殺。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P7Lbfo2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP7Lbfo2.png&h=d03827e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n涉嫌箍頸的黑警林偉榮<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OQQZpf6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOQQZpf6.png&h=4c4fa5ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黑警馬振康指拘捕的士司機時，對方不斷掙扎"},{"pid":"923ff34b3af48539a40f706dab38802d5a0b4a6a","tid":1094657,"uid":44358,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T12:58:18.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b3484bb9da92a8ae3e000fcca77a6718f2d0503","tid":1094657,"uid":34949,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T13:07:44.000Z","msg":"推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfd6020ed076f2824d2735a9b8554698441106f7","tid":1094657,"uid":9193,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T13:21:23.000Z","msg":"冇人理 證明而家五毛多到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7f773585b3f8571c2f52467e3f465f585f0afb7","tid":1094657,"uid":171107,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T13:23:15.000Z","msg":"拖到啲證人記唔返